3c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e答：会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e答个题有这么难吗？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563780364,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"90be450b7f3b6c5888c9b347708aef96","url_token":"li-bang-65","name":"180天后","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/f0a2434abbebe09a02b6b3f6de4caa4e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/f0a2434abbebe09a02b6b3f6de4caa4e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/90be450b7f3b6c5888c9b347708aef96","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563780364","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276079,"updated_time":1546277690,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":89,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我知道你会错，我只想看到你错的水平。对不起，我真的太失望了。请取消关注，严重质疑答主动机，原因如下：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.不努力。如果是追求真理的人，会去查阅资料，完善自己的证明过程。而答主的答案看不到任何查阅资料的痕迹。看起来更像是课堂上偶尔想到了有意思的方法，然后随便写出来玩玩。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.爱演戏。答主想必知道自己证明是很可笑的，但是在知乎上提问之后，获得了极大的关注，给他带来了快感，然后为了追求刺激，连续运用定时公布求关注，给教授邮箱表真实等手段，进一步欺骗，提升真实性，为自己获得更多关注。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.不善良。提问之后，各大科班出身的大佬都或尖锐或委婉给出了证明这事的难度和不可能性。答主自己证明正确与否，应该心知肚明。如果一个善良谦逊的学生，会第一时间给出证明结果，让各位指出问题，毕竟这么多人等着看，利用这么多人的信任，或者有意把自己当猴或者戏猴绝非善良之举，动机不在纯洁。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网络是虚拟的也是真实的，他人的关注能给你带来一时的快感，但真才实学和人格品质才能让自己荣耀一生。欲戴其冠必承其重，孩子做学问之前先做一个善良而又努力的人吧。网络可以成就你，但也可以毁了你。你现在好好的，需要感谢我们伟大的知乎网友。但是今后我们再也不允许出现第二个这样的人。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560064304,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3568e819a6e6a5b1b71cf506149c9b8d","url_token":"lazxh","name":"lazxh","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3568e819a6e6a5b1b71cf506149c9b8d","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560064304","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545806107,"updated_time":1545806107,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":613,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这位同学你好，作为一名高中数学老师，我深感惭愧。如果我的学生告诉我他可以证明哥德巴赫猜想，我绝不会同意他保送什么清北，我会亲自与哈佛等著名学府联系，终身教授不是问题。（内心独白：滚犊子，先把圆锥曲线和数列给我弄明白吧）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559408610,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c5444b59940bcb7c53b4263aa3b88cdb","url_token":"jiang-rui-feng-45-79","name":"姜维","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/0d1a77531580571fe48a49a22b174b25_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/0d1a77531580571fe48a49a22b174b25_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c5444b59940bcb7c53b4263aa3b88cdb","user_type":"people","headline":"不务正业的理科生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559408610","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545724449,"updated_time":1546275089,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":567,"content":"\u003cp\u003e果然我真的太善良了，对于我确实不该劝民科从良的，各位圣母们脸可疼？\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e几句话送给你：井蛙不可语海，夏虫不可语冰；朝菌不知晦朔，蟪蛄不知春秋。小小年纪怕是不知道哥猜在数学界的分量，也怕是不知道前人做过多少功课，只不过看着猜想通俗易懂就觉得证明也应该通俗易懂。说好听点叫初生牛犊不怕虎，说难听点叫不是蠢就是坏。话又说回来，这个年纪无论是蠢还是坏都还有救，可千万别不听劝，沦为民科吧那群货色可就晚了。要是觉得我的话说重了，可以先给你学校的教数学竞赛的老师看看，如果他有耐心那应该用不了几分钟就能给你指出错误，省的到时候发出来被一群人挑错，毕竟这个年纪也挺爱面子的，下不来台也不好。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559711039,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d35046323f0a767d5768c67a16a754f6","url_token":"jiang-jiang-jiang-nan-wu-yan-zu","name":"EMINJAY","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-88c396d9343e9e76dadcb3995ea175e4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-88c396d9343e9e76dadcb3995ea175e4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d35046323f0a767d5768c67a16a754f6","user_type":"people","headline":"努力变得与众不同","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559711039","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545753797,"updated_time":1545753797,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":744,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这哥们让我感觉他在做一个社会实验。。。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559430029,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5502781558d085f80d3f3c1fd6351e50","url_token":"ding-ming-55-55","name":"Phoenix Cat","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/e01994d6f7c30267f887d3d134d07fbe_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/e01994d6f7c30267f887d3d134d07fbe_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5502781558d085f80d3f3c1fd6351e50","user_type":"people","headline":"继续尝试退乎","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559430029","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545726190,"updated_time":1545726190,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":653,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不太行，哥德巴赫猜想几十年来已经被很多高中、初中甚至小学毕业的人证明过很多次了，你可以去百度贴吧甚至在知乎相关问题下找到短则几行多至数十页的证明，这种东西怎么能让你进入清北呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":558294514,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1ca20a0549dd509cd281fad084b31a60","url_token":"qian-sen-56-66","name":"浅森","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-167ce5d79a50f183fe5fb4091725332a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-167ce5d79a50f183fe5fb4091725332a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1ca20a0549dd509cd281fad084b31a60","user_type":"people","headline":"刚入坑的生物狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/558294514","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-382b59bd9ef3c57f9051daa800f9a6d3_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545582111,"updated_time":1545973877,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":454,"content":"\u003cp\u003e12.28  与问题和回答本身都无关的更新\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e突然这个问题就有了这么多回答，就想说，对面是高中生也好，民科也罢，怎么强调问题有多难都好，但还是要对事不对人，不要人身攻击。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但同时也再劝题主一句，千万不要因为这么多人表示反对，就有了“我下次做一个更难的打你们的脸”的想法。数学研究有路可走，就是去老老实实地学习前人的理论。感兴趣也可以翻一翻数学史，了解一些光鲜成就之外的数学研究。也更有助于让自己知道数学并不容易。要知道仅仅一个微积分的严谨化，一代一代数学家就花了近二百年。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是如果还是想骑自行车上月球，原地打转尚且还是好结果;你可能会摔得很惨。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下为原答案：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前在做这个方向的数学家虽然不是很多，但据我了解也是有一些人在做的。我不是想说王侯将相真的就是有种，而是科学研究的的确确很专业很专业，需要大量知识积累和科学方法训练，想跨过这些去做科研，几乎没有可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不知道您是否看过陈景润先生关于“1+2”的证明。事实上，不要说1+2，即使是最早的9+9这样相对而言很弱的结论，就已经不是用的初等方法了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我知识储备不足，看不懂这些证明。不过楼主既然想证明哥德巴赫猜想，自然应该研读过前人的工作，至少也是应该有基本了解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我随便贴两页陈景润先生的工作\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dddaeeef4e26b67543c985403946157d_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1369\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3a222e03a9918afc67f162874d4c3663_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1369\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dddaeeef4e26b67543c985403946157d_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1369'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1369\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3a222e03a9918afc67f162874d4c3663_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1369\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dddaeeef4e26b67543c985403946157d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dddaeeef4e26b67543c985403946157d_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d6cf75de4cb4a5af00d5229fb0e7da_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1369\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-edc810c39fdeaa73cdb1727ceae4777e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1369\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d6cf75de4cb4a5af00d5229fb0e7da_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1369'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1369\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-edc810c39fdeaa73cdb1727ceae4777e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1369\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d6cf75de4cb4a5af00d5229fb0e7da_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d6cf75de4cb4a5af00d5229fb0e7da_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e图二中提到了“较为简单的计算方法”证明了引理8，再来看一看它到底有多“简单”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8332074613f09f32d7f8be3fab510138_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1354\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c7576cee343005f2fab7e88f769ce67a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1354\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8332074613f09f32d7f8be3fab510138_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1354'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1354\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c7576cee343005f2fab7e88f769ce67a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1354\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8332074613f09f32d7f8be3fab510138_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8332074613f09f32d7f8be3fab510138_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ef5b77162f3fc68f02d18a8905a55695_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1354\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-afba9fe7a93abf366f567b547252cf52_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1354\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ef5b77162f3fc68f02d18a8905a55695_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1354'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1354\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-afba9fe7a93abf366f567b547252cf52_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1354\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ef5b77162f3fc68f02d18a8905a55695_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ef5b77162f3fc68f02d18a8905a55695_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e确实，相对于下面这种画风的，简单不少\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9a92fe88481cf392a83a2f4abd0aaa09_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1892\" data-rawheight=\"2862\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df24c8f1cf33bd20a24896932599bace_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1892\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9a92fe88481cf392a83a2f4abd0aaa09_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1892'%20height='2862'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1892\" data-rawheight=\"2862\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df24c8f1cf33bd20a24896932599bace_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1892\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9a92fe88481cf392a83a2f4abd0aaa09_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9a92fe88481cf392a83a2f4abd0aaa09_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这部分工作，至今仍被认为是筛法中相当漂亮的一个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我没有别的意思，我其实是想说，如果您用的是这种画风的方法，不提这些东西是在哪里学到的，就说结果：您大概可以在哈佛斯坦福MIT等名校里随便挑一个去做教授了。如果是初等方法，那么这么多数学家在尝试证明弱化的哥德巴赫猜想时，都没有如此，您是否有信心这样独辟蹊径地去寻求“正确”？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至于发到哪怎么发可能会有哪些结果，其他答主都说得很好了，我就不赘述了。不过提一点，我们学校物理学院有一个“交流群”，就是社会上的一些科学工作者和在校生会在特定的时间以特定的方式讨论一些问题。楼主可以看一看是否有学校在数学方面有这种讨论群。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我对数学前沿工作了解很少，只是感兴趣看了一些内容，如有错误请指正。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=60\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=20\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
